text: Minzhong or Min Zhong may refer to: * Central Min, a group of Min dialects spoken in central Fujian, China * Minzhong, Zhongshan, a town in Guangdong, China * Fuzhou, a city on the location of the Qin-era Minzhong prefecture * Yu Minzhong (1714–1779), an official of the Qing dynasty in China
title: Minzhong (disambiguation)
